description:
Priestess Lust is a short stealth game in which you try to escape captivity from a multi-floor
dungeon, with or without your allies. Also you get fucked if you fail.

v0.0.1.description: This is not a real release as I am too skill issued by Unity to make a client mod for the game. Nevertheless, I have created an APWorld which should logically function correctly.
